  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Fight Tab</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_icon.png?5179c5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/32px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"dablink\"><i>For the filter in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a>, see <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Weapons_Filter\" title=\"Weapons Filter\">Weapons Filter</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Armor_Filter\" title=\"Armor Filter\">Armor Filter</a>.</i></span></dd></dl>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Icon_Fight.png\" class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Icon_Fight.png?e67291\" width=\"105\" height=\"128\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Icon_Fight.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tab Icon</div></div></div>\n<div><b>“</b><span>En garde!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Webber\" title=\"Webber\">Webber</a></p>\n</div> \n<p><b>Fight</b> items and structures can be obtained from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a>, in the Fight tab with the Crossed Swords icon on the left-hand side.\n</p>\n<ul><li>See all the <b><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Weapons\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Weapons\">Weapons</a></b> in the game.</li>\n<li>See all the <b><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Armor\">Armors</a></b> in the game.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Downloadable_Content\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Gift_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Gift Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Gift_Icon.png/32px-Gift_Icon.png?8b4efa\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Downloadable Content</span></h2>\n<p>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Reign of Giants\">Reign of Giants</a></i> DLC, the player can craft <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Weather_Pain\" title=\"Weather Pain\">Weather Pains</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Scalemail\" title=\"Scalemail\">Scalemails</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Morning_Star\" title=\"Morning Star\">Morning Stars</a>, and while playing as <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wigfrid\" title=\"Wigfrid\">Wigfrid</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Battle_Spear\" title=\"Battle Spear\">Battle Spears</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Battle_Helm\" title=\"Battle Helm\">Battle Helms</a> in the Fight Tab.\n</p><p>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Poison_Spear\" title=\"Poison Spear\">Poison Spears</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seashell_Suit\" title=\"Seashell Suit\">Seashell Suits</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone_Suit\" title=\"Limestone Suit\">Limestone Suits</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cactus_Armor\" title=\"Cactus Armor\">Cactus Armors</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Horned_Helmet\" title=\"Horned Helmet\">Horned Helmets</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Poison_Dart\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Poison Dart\">Poison Darts</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Coconade\" title=\"Coconade\">Coconades</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spear_Gun\" title=\"Spear Gun\">Spear Guns</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cutlass_Supreme\" title=\"Cutlass Supreme\">Cutlass Supremes</a> were added to the Fight Tab.\n</p><p>The <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC introduces <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Halberd\" title=\"Halberd\">Halberds</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork_Bat\" title=\"Cork Bat\">Cork Bats</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Weevole_Mantle\" title=\"Weevole Mantle\">Weevole Mantles</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mant_Mask\" title=\"Mant Mask\">Mant Masks</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mant_Suit\" title=\"Mant Suit\">Mant Suits</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fancy_Helmet\" title=\"Fancy Helmet\">Fancy Helmets</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tin_Suit\" title=\"Tin Suit\">Tin Suits</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blunderbuss\" title=\"Blunderbuss\">Blunderbusses</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Craftable_Items_and_Structures\">Craftable Items and Structures</span></h2>\n<p>The following items and structures can be crafted in the Fight Tab:\n</p>\n<div><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\"><img alt=\"Spear\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spear.png?63081f\" width=\"78\" height=\"78\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\">Spear</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ham_Bat\" title=\"Ham Bat\"><img alt=\"Ham Bat\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ham_Bat.png?5d0157\" width=\"78\" height=\"78\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ham_Bat\" title=\"Ham Bat\">Ham Bat</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Grass_Suit\" title=\"Grass Suit\"><img alt=\"Grass Suit\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Grass_Suit.png?ea9b5d\" width=\"78\" height=\"78\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Grass_Suit\" title=\"Grass Suit\">Grass Suit</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Log_Suit\" title=\"Log Suit\"><img alt=\"Log Suit\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Log_Suit.png?52bcd2\" width=\"78\" height=\"78\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Log_Suit\" title=\"Log Suit\">Log Suit</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Marble_Suit\" title=\"Marble Suit\"><img alt=\"Marble Suit\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Marble_Suit.png?6019ed\" width=\"78\" height=\"78\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Marble_Suit\" title=\"Marble Suit\">Marble Suit</a></div>\n\t\t</div><