  "title": "Fight Tab",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve|Reign of Giants|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{for|the filter in [[Don't Starve Together]]|Weapons Filter|Armor Filter}}\n[[File:Icon Fight.png|right|thumb|Tab Icon]]\n{{Quote|En garde!|Webber}} \n\n'''Fight''' items and structures can be obtained from [[Crafting]], in the Fight tab with the Crossed Swords icon on the left-hand side.\n* See all the '''[[Weapons]]''' in the game.\n* See all the '''[[Armor]]s''' in the game.\n\n==[[File:Gift Icon.png|32px]] Downloadable Content==\nIn the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' DLC, the player can craft [[Weather Pain]]s, [[Scalemail]]s, [[Morning Star]]s, and while playing as [[Wigfrid]], [[Battle Spear]]s, and [[Battle Helm]]s in the Fight Tab.\n\nIn the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC, [[Poison Spear]]s, [[Seashell Suit]]s, [[Limestone Suit]]s, [[Cactus Armor]]s, [[Horned Helmet]]s, [[Poison Dart]]s, [[Coconade]]s, [[Spear Gun]]s, and [[Cutlass Supreme]]s were added to the Fight Tab.\n\nThe ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC introduces [[Halberd]]s, [[Cork Bat]]s, [[Weevole Mantle]]s, [[Mant Mask]]s, [[Mant Suit]]s, [[Fancy Helmet]]s, [[Tin Suit]]s and [[Blunderbuss]]es.\n\n==Craftable Items and Structures==\nThe following items and structures can be crafted in the Fight Tab:\n\n<div style=\"clear:both; font-weight: bold\"><gallery columns=\"6\" position=\"center\" widths=\"78\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\n\nSpear.png|link=Spear|[[Spear]]\nHam Bat.png|link=Ham Bat|[[Ham Bat]]\nGrass Suit.png|link=Grass Suit|[[Grass Suit]]\nLog Suit.png|link=Log Suit|[[Log Suit]]\nMarble Suit.png|link=Marble Suit|[[Marble Suit]]\nFootball Helmet.png|link=Football Helmet|[[Football Helmet]]\nSleep Dart.png|link=Sleep Dart|[[Sleep Dart]]\nFire Dart.png|link=Fire Dart|[[Fire Dart]]\nBlow Dart.png|link=Blow Dart|[[Blow Dart]]\nBoomerang.png|link=Boomerang|[[Boomerang]]\nBee Mine.png|link=Bee Mine|[[Bee Mine]]\nTooth Trap.png|link=Tooth Trap|[[Tooth Trap]]\nWeather Pain.png|link=Weather Pain|[[Weather Pain]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}\nScalemail.png|link=Scalemail|[[Scalemail]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}\nMorning Star.png|link=Morning_Star|[[Morning Star]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}\nBattle Spear.png|link=Battle_Spear|[[Battle Spear]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Wigfrid Portrait|Wigfrid}}\nBattle Helm.png|link=Battle_Helm|[[Battle Helm]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Wigfrid Portrait|Wigfrid}}\nPoison Spear.png|link=Poison Spear|[[Poison Spear]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSeashell Suit.png|link=Seashell Suit|[[Seashell Suit]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nLimestone Suit.png|link=Limestone Suit|[[Limestone Suit]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nCactus Armor.png|link=Cactus Armor|[[Cactus Armor]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nHorned Helmet.png|link=Horned Helmet|[[Horned Helmet]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nPoison Dart.png|link=Poison Dart|[[Poison Dart]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nCoconade.png|link=Coconade|[[Coconade]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSpear Gun.png|link=Spear_Gun|[[Spear Gun]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nCutlass Supreme.png|link=Cutlass Supreme|[[Cutlass Supreme]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nHalberd.png|link=Halberd|[[Halberd]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nCork Bat.png|link=Cork Bat|[[Cork Bat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nWeevole Mantle.png|link=Weevole Mantle|[[Weevole Mantle]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nMant Mask.png|link=Mant Mask|[[Mant Mask]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nMant Suit.png|link=Mant Suit|[[Mant Suit]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nFancy Helmet.png|link=Fancy Helmet|[[Fancy Helmet]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nTin Suit.png|link=Tin Suit|[[Tin Suit]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nBlunderbuss.png|link=Blunderbuss|[[Blunderbuss]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\n\n</gallery></div>\n\n=={{Pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia==\n* The Fight Tab icon is available for use on [[Steam Content|Steam]] as a chat emoticon.\n\n{{Tabs}}\n[[ru:Бой]]\n[[ko:전투 탭]]\n__NOTOC__"
